Message.message: I was just trying to hide from the world.
I spent a lot of time playing a game called Castlemouse.
Everything seemed to be slipping away from me.
The world seemed full of fear.
Everything was falling apart for me at once.
I don't remember that time very well.
I don't even remember exactly how Castlemouse went.
Many things were set in motion at that time.
Many unexpected chains of events, not all bad.
I'm doing a lot better now.
Also, Castlemouse is a much better game than this - you should track it down.
Music: Broken - Fit and the Conniptions (music.conniptions.org)
